INSERT INTO
                        prover_jobs_fri (
                            l1_batch_number,
                            circuit_id,
                            circuit_blob_url,
                            aggregation_round,
                            sequence_number,
                            depth,
                            is_node_final_proof,
                            protocol_version,
                            status,
                            created_at,
                            updated_at,
                            protocol_version_patch
                        )
                    VALUES
                        ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, 'queued', NOW(), NOW(), $9)
                    ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number, aggregation_round, circuit_id, depth, sequence_number) DO
                    UPDATE
                    SET
                        updated_at = NOW()
